collections.name: Avits Anne
collections.description:
Do you think you truly understand cats? Wrong! They’re not just about eating, sleeping, and messing up your house. Some cats, like Avits Hanie, have far greater missions—like protecting the entire universe! But don’t rush to expect a perfect hero...

Avits Hanie—a cat with blue fur, a head full of ideas… and a stomach that’s always growling! One day, he accidentally activated a strange collar, opening a space portal. From a peaceful house cat living with his bowl of fish, Avits now plunges into thrilling adventures, encounters bizarre creatures, and faces a mysterious foe named Shadow Claw—who loves destruction but has… psychological issues.

Funny, dangerous, and sometimes… a complete mess, Avits’s journey is the story of a small cat daring to dream big. He may not be perfect, but who ever said heroes have to be perfect, right?"

collections.name: Komorebi
collections.description:
''Komorebi'' is a collection of photographs shot that i take in my lay over around the world.

Komorebi is a Japanese word that refers to the interplay of sunlight as it filters through the leaves of trees.

Everything I tasted, smelled, and felt while exploring the world is in this album. Seeing it sometimes makes me relive these emotions.

I dedicate this collection to myself, striving to find my light amidst all the challenges I have faced.

collections.name: VladasMoods
collections.description: I really enjoyed creating something that wasn’t as “huge” as the artwork I usually make. I love big, detailed pieces, but sometimes I get bored working on the same one for weeks. That’s how I got an idea to starte Vlada’s Mood collection. Sometimes, when I feel like creating something specific just for fun and experimenting, I’ll add it to the Vlada’s Mood collection. This collection can be anything—no rules, no special themes, just Vlada’s mood.
